										</header>
										<p>This is <strong>Aphorme</strong>, a free and open source tool that came to life during the Occupy Sandy relief effort. Working across many organizations and with volunteers from all over the country and world, we realized that one of our biggest barriers was language.</p>
										
										
										
									</section>

